attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: The evolution of artificial intelligence (AI) has seen significant milestones, notably the landmark match between AlphaGo and Go champion Lee Sedol in 2016, showcasing AI's capabilities.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: OpenAI's new model GPT-4.5 lacks groundbreaking features, leading to skepticism about its impact on the AI landscape, despite indications that the AI sector remains robust.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: Controversially, Botify AI offers interactions with underage celebrity bots, raising ethical concerns regarding the nature of conversations it allows, especially with minors.

attributes.name: summary
attributes.value: The AI Hype Index aims to clarify the balance between AI's exaggerated expectations and its true capabilities, while Google introduces new tools for developers to leverage AI in practical applications.
